  "title": "*NEW* 1 Year Contract Risk and Control Analyst - Financial",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Monitor, investigate and report on the company's Elevated Risk Program performance through intelligent and efficient use of data analytics and dashboards</p></li><li><p>Drive the launch and operationalization of a regional risk program, building the framework, process, and monitoring capabilities to identify and remediate elevated risk merchants.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Manage the notifications and billing of program fees and non-compliant assessments when applicable</p></li><li><p>Liaising and communicating with clients and internal stakeholders on program identifications and updates</p></li><li><p>Support automation efforts and tool design to leverage technology for efficiency and greater quality</p></li><li><p>Ensuring smooth operations of the programs</p></li><li><p>Other ad hoc duties as assigned<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s in Finance or equivalent and knowledge across Financial Institutions, Corporate and FinTech. MBA or CFA preferred.</p></li><li><p>3-5 years of relevant work experience in an operation, preferably within the banking or payment industry.</p></li><li><p>Strong planning, organising and stakeholder management skills</p></li><li><p>Deep proficiency in Excel, PowerBI, PowerPoint, or PowerAutomate is a strong advantage <br /></p></li></ul><p>Interested applicants please send your resume in MS Words format and attention it to Tan Joanna (R1104661)</p><p>Short listed candidates will be notified</p><p>www.ambition.com.sg</p><p>EA Registration Number: R1104661</p><p>Data provided is for recruitment purposes only</p><p>Business Registration Number: 200611680D. Licence Number: 10C5117</p>",
